The class to generate the main view tree

Version:
visda_v0.4 Version Log: visda_v0.2 (08/30/2005): The file is created and basic view tree is implemented. visda_v0.3 (09/29/2005): Implement multiple data and multiple analysis view; add history log; Node can be deleted. visda_v0.4 (10/29/2005): Separate the results into 'Clusters' and 'Levels' nodes.
